Interface PagedQueryResult<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the underlying model, like category or product.
    All Superinterfaces:
    PagedResult<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PagedQueryResultDsl

    public interface PagedQueryResult<T>
extends PagedResult<T>
    A container for query responses which contains a subset of the matching values.
